### 3. Blueprint Extraction Prompt (Fix: Copy so sánh từ gốc)

#### [MODIFY] [system_extract_blueprint_mystery.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_extract_blueprint_mystery.txt)

- **Giữ nguyên**: `mainstream_theory`, `counter_evidence` (dữ liệu thực tế)
- **Fix 1**: Field `comparisons` chỉ ghi "so sánh với ai, về khía cạnh nào" — KHÔNG copy câu so sánh/ẩn dụ nguyên văn
- **Fix 2**: Rule: "Do NOT extract analogies, metaphors, or rhetorical comparisons. Extract ONLY discrete factual data."
- **Fix 3**: `detailed_facts` cấm entries dạng "compared X to Y using analogy Z"

